org.eclipse.modisco.jee.ejbjar.EjbJar11
Interface MethodType

public interface MethodType

A representation of the model object 'Method Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Description
  • Ejb Name
  • Method Intf
  • Method Name
  • Method Params
  • Id
